  "title": "Cloud Cost Reporting",
  "content": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\">\n<p>Cloud Cost Reporting helps you to monitor your cloud spending and simplifies the configuration of various cloud providers. </p>\n<p>This section covers the following topics: </p>\n<ul style=\"padding-left: 0px;\"><li style=\"margin-left: 28px; position: relative;\"><a href=\"/doc/423/26.1/cloudoperations\" title=\"Cloud Operations\">Cloud operations</a></li><li style=\"margin-left: 28px; position: relative;\"><a href=\"/doc/423/26.1/showbackreports\" title=\"Cost governance\">Cloud cost reports</a></li></ul>\n<h2 id=\"Related_topcis\"><a id=\"Related_topics\" name=\"Related_topics\" title=\"Related topics\"></a>Related topics</h2>\n<ul style=\"padding-left: 0px;\"><li style=\"margin-left: 28px; position: relative;\">For information about how to configure cloud cost data integration, see <a href=\"/doc/423/26.1/cgrointegrations\" title=\"Cloud cost data providers\">Cloud cost data providers</a>.</li><li style=\"margin-left: 28px; position: relative;\">\n<p style=\"text-align:start; margin-bottom:13px\">To troubleshoot issues related to Cloud Cost Reporting, refer to logs related to the following microservices:</p>\n<ul style=\"padding-left: 0px;\"><li style=\"margin-left: 40px; position: relative;\"><code style='font-size:0.866666em; color:#323435; font-family:Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, \"Roboto Mono\", \"Courier New\", \"Ubuntu Mono\", monospace; font-weight:400; padding:0px; border-radius:3px; border:none; word-break:break-word'><font face=\"monospace\">costpolicy</font></code></li><li style=\"margin-left: 40px; position: relative;\"><code style='font-size:0.866666em; color:#323435; font-family:Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, \"Roboto Mono\", \"Courier New\", \"Ubuntu Mono\", monospace; font-weight:400; padding:0px; border-radius:3px; border:none; word-break:break-word'><font face=\"monospace\">insights</font></code></li><li style=\"margin-left: 40px; position: relative;\"><code style='font-size:0.866666em; color:#323435; font-family:Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, \"Roboto Mono\", \"Courier New\", \"Ubuntu Mono\", monospace; font-weight:400; padding:0px; border-radius:3px; border:none; word-break:break-word'>insights-gateway</code></li><li style=\"margin-left: 40px; position: relative;\"><code style='font-size:0.866666em; color:#323435; font-family:Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, \"Roboto Mono\", \"Courier New\", \"Ubuntu Mono\", monospace; font-weight:400; padding:0px; border-radius:3px; border:none; word-break:break-word'>policy-gateway</code></li><li style=\"margin-left: 40px; position: relative;\"><code style='font-size:0.866666em; color:#323435; font-family:Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, \"Roboto Mono\", \"Courier New\", \"Ubuntu Mono\", monospace; font-weight:400; padding:0px; border-radius:3px; border:none; word-break:break-word'>showback</code></li><li style=\"margin-left: 40px; position: relative;\"><code style='font-size:0.866666em; color:#323435; font-family:Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, \"Roboto Mono\", \"Courier New\", \"Ubuntu Mono\", monospace; font-weight:400; padding:0px; border-radius:3px; border:none; word-break:break-word'>showback-gateway</code></li></ul>\n</li></ul>\n</div>",
